{"tid":1616290,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮聯署:要求美國禁止和中共銀行進行交易！","createTime":"2019-10-03T10:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T10:58:22.000Z","uid":233000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe81d74faefb79fefe7265cd6d6a147477d2d17","tid":1616290,"uid":233000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:57:10.000Z","msg":"要求美國宣布禁止和中共銀行進行交易<br />\n<br />\n經濟的持續發展給了中共統治的基礎，不過中共敗局已定，現今中國大陸民怨四起，黨內分裂加劇，香港全民對抗中共殖民暴政，戰火可能蔓延到中國大陸，再加上中國經濟全面滑落，金融體系積重難返，已經是朝不保夕，所以禁止和中國進行銀行交易是唯一的方法！中共的經濟崩潰後，希望美國繼續孤立中共，立即要求聯合國、WTO等國際組織把中共踢出去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requested-united-states-ban-trading-bank-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequested-united-states-ban-trading-bank-china&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=427f4f04\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requested-united-states-ban-trading-bank-china</a>"},{"pid":"d227db2d9c8444693249d67cc919ae3e42a1a39d","tid":1616290,"uid":274141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:58:22.000Z","msg":"請問呢個叫咩魔法?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1616275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1616275</a>"}]}